# Update Java in Remote machine 

* Initially java version 1.7 was installed

* Download Java from https://www.java.com/en/download/linux_manual.jsp
	Select "Linux x64"

* Then, inside my server I have unpacked with:
	tar -xvf jre-8u151-linux-x64.tar.gz

* And then I have add the following line to my .bashrc file:
	export PATH=/home/kkuma12s/jre1.8.0_151/bin:$PATH

* Source bashrc file to make sure that changes affect

